item.title: Webclient Error! Rep++!
item.dc:creator: @RS2BullDog RS2BullDog
item.description:
@RS2BullDog wrote:

Skiire:

It means that you compiled your classes using a specific JDK, but then you ran them under an older version of JDK.

Either that or he hasn’t uploaded the jar onto his website, so the website cannot find the JAR so it won’t run.

I think that’s it
